sentences.english: Objective To observe the efficacy of Blattella germanica control with gel bait and poison powder.
sentences.chinese: 目的觀察套餐法控制酒店德國小蠊的效果。

sentences.english: Objective To observe the effect of Jieyuan gel bait on killing Blattella germanica.
sentences.chinese: 目的觀察潔園滅蟑餌劑現場殺滅德國小蠊的效果。

sentences.english: Objective: determination of the resistance of Germen cockroach in passenger train to common insecticides.
sentences.chinese: 目的旅客列車德國小蠊對常用殺蟲劑的抗性測定。

sentences.english: The morphological features of Biattlla germanica cerci were observed under scanning electron microscope.
sentences.chinese: 本實驗用掃描電鏡觀察了德國小蠊尾須的細微結構。

sentences.english: Objective To observe the efficacy of 2% acetaniprid gel bait against Blattella germanica.
sentences.chinese: 目的觀察2%啶蟲脒殺蟑膠餌對德國小蠊的殺滅效果。

sentences.english: Objective To observe the effect of Premise cockroach gel bait on killing Blattella germanica.
sentences.chinese: 目的觀察拜滅士殺蟑膠餌現場殺滅德國小蠊的效果。

sentences.english: The ultrastructure of maxillary palpi of Blattella germanica were observed with scanning electron microscope.
sentences.chinese: 用掃描電鏡觀察了德國小蠊下顎須的超微結構。

sentences.english: Pyrethroids used to control Blattella germanica on ships should be attended.
sentences.chinese: 選用擬除蟲菊酯防制艦艇上的德國小蠊應引起注意。

sentences.english: Objective To study effective methods for controlling Blattella germanica in special places.
sentences.chinese: 目的研究特殊場所控制德國小蠊侵害的方法。

sentences.english: Conclusion SH is an effective pathogenic Strain to control Blattella germanica.
sentences.chinese: 結論SH菌株是防治德國小蠊的有效致病菌株。

sentences.english: Objective To observe the efficacy of DDVP aerosol against Blattella germanica.
sentences.chinese: 目的瞭解敵敵畏熱煙霧劑對德國小蠊的殺滅效果。
